                  >
                </p>`
  },
  {
    title: `Responsive website<br />
                  for an outsourcing company`,
    content: `<p>
                  A website with SVG animations and highest accessibility
                  standards. PSD by <a
                    onclick="trackOutboundLink('https://heavyform.com/'); return false;"
                    href="https://heavyform.com/"
